{"tid":905291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【心碎至死】86歲婆婆撞死小女孩極內疚 受折磨多月逝世","createTime":"2018-11-17T04:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T05:31:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae2203e361f54e4a6812a8365d3816d3da8464c","tid":905291,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"澳洲昆士蘭省陽光海岸一名86歲老婦不慎駕車撞死一名6歲女童，她為此自責不已，更生無可戀放棄治療，最終在本周三逝世。她臨死前跟丈夫說︰「我殺了一個孩子，不想再活下去」。<br />\n這宗悲劇發生在今年6月17日，米里亞姆（Miriam Paton）在一個購物中心停車場倒車時，不慎撞到英迪（Indie Armstrong）及她的姐姐、祖母，3人同告受傷，最後英迪身亡。<br />\n米里亞姆被控危險駕駛，意外發生後兩天，她因腰椎骨折送院，之後更併發肺炎，在車禍後大部份時間都在醫院度過，但因為英迪之死，她「決定不接受治療」。<br />\n米里亞姆的90歲丈夫佩頓（Stuart Paton）稱，太太一生都很愛小朋友，曾任小學教師長達50年，她無法接受自己害死英迪，心痛難擋。「她傷心欲絕，想及自己害死小女孩感到難以承受，她想死。」他坦言永遠不會忘記兩人談及此事時，妻子面上流露的痛苦神色。米里亞姆周三逝世時，醫院員工都為她落淚。<br />\n英迪的父親表示已收到米里亞姆的死訊，他說︰「我們沒甚麼可再說的了，說甚麼也不能令她復生。這段時間真的艱難。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181116/large/1542372828_c6cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181116%2Flarge%2F1542372828_c6cc.jpg&h=5b82024c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181117/58920833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58920833&d=uYzQBpRLOc79lpwGqeW%2Bx4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fcef085f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58920833&h=a4952035\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181117/58920833</a>"},{"pid":"1ecce7a147898bc305ff8a51569b6a650c4139d2","tid":905291,"uid":21886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"臨尾香系列"},{"pid":"6721862f463a112ba53d24d38169888bbf8f7611","tid":905291,"uid":55279,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"最危險的駕駛因素<br />\n<br />\n老<br />\n<br />\n女人<br />\n<br />\n老女人"},{"pid":"bb792c474d6fd3233ec95b2d6a8f0da61aec3acc","tid":905291,"uid":95397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6721862f463a112ba53d24d38169888bbf8f7611","tid":905291,"uid":55279,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"最危險的駕駛因素<br />\n<br />\n老<br />\n<br />\n女人<br />\n<br />\n老女人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"中曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92b8122e4dfe6799e35127f1b06a6ec582697ba","tid":905291,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"仲差八十年命點賠俾人"},{"pid":"686be6e9aa94728f4208ed5be8cf5b5bce3ec6a5","tid":905291,"uid":37297,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"86歲刀叉都揸唔穩啦, 仲揸乜嘢車"},{"pid":"99159ef66171deedc1a975b2513470e00eed7bf7","tid":905291,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"叫佢去支那住返半年<br />\n<br />\n包佢老年無憂"},{"pid":"7153313dd4f5f4920c222a82432988d6017716d4","tid":905291,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c12a97384905bb525d28a41140e13d5bcf7365","tid":905291,"uid":177047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6721862f463a112ba53d24d38169888bbf8f7611","tid":905291,"uid":55279,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"最危險的駕駛因素<br />\n<br />\n老<br />\n<br />\n女人<br />\n<br />\n老女人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"馬路三寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}